Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 29 Apr 2025

GOTronome is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our application.

1. No Data Collection
We do not collect, store, or share any personal or non-personal data from users of the GOTronome app. Your use of the app is entirely anonymous.

2. No Ads or In-App Purchases
The app contains no advertisements and does not offer or require in-app purchases. You will not be subject to any form of advertising or tracking.

3. Open Source
GOTronome is an open-source application. You can view the complete source code at https://github.com/depasca/GOTronome, which ensures full transparency in how the app functions.

4. Changes to This Policy
Although this policy is unlikely to change due to the simplicity of our app, we reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy. Any changes will be posted here with an updated effective date.

5. Contact
If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, feel free to contact us at https://github.com/depasca/GOTronome/issues.
